This plugin will be home of all ChoiceMatch's profile-related developments.

July 30, 2014
First version only differentiates client and biz profile pages over default profile fields.
For client, here are the profile fields that can be set:
-My display name
-Location
-Contact email
-Telephone
-Mobile phone
For biz, here are the profile fields that can be set:
-My display name
-About me
-Brief description
-Location
-Skills
-Contact email
-Telephone
-Mobile phone
-website
-Twitter username

For each user type, only those profile fields set are shown on profile page.